<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ chàng yī zhī gē wèi nǐ men sòng xíng, zhù nǐ men yī lù shùn fēng.
 jīn tiān fēn shǒu hòu, bù jiǔ hái xiāng féng, wǒ men hái shì tóng gōng.
 wàng bù le nǐ duì wǒ men de zhūn zhūn jiào dǎo, wàng bù le wǒ men xiāng chù shí de zhēn chéng.
 lí kāi zhè lǐ bié wàng jì dài qiú, nǐ men yī lù yào duō bǎo zhòng.</lyrics>
<title>wèi nǐ sòng xíng 迦南289</title>
<hymn_number>289</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>